ên đà phá sản. Thêm vào đó, bác sĩ Park Won Jang bắt đầu bị rụng tóc. Vợ anh là Sa Mo Rim lại chỉ tin tưởng các chương trình y tế trên truyền hình hơn là khả năng của chồng. Liệu bác sĩ Park Won Jang sẽ làm gì để xoay chuyển được tình thế?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"154522","season":1,"vote_average":7.7,"vote_count":9},"modified":"2022-06-17T05:00:33.000Z","cast":["Lee Seo-jin","Ra Mi-ran","Cha Chung-hwa","Shin Eun-jung","Kim Kwang-kyu","Kim Kang-hoon","Jung Hyung-suk","Joo Woo-yeon","Seo Bum-june"],"director":["Seo Jun-beom"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lee Seo-jin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee Seo-jin","tmdb_id":77282,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s5KginY3G9ZmqsgiOKmx9mto6Vx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/77282"},{"name":"Ra Mi-ran","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ra Mi-ran","tmdb_id":980225,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/45jkWK6vQpQo32FsbGMSDrZig62.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/980225"},{"name":"Cha Chung-hwa","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Cha Chung-hwa","tmdb_id":2533271,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/glTQksczMwEHUYFaKkLnwMRuVr3.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2533271"},{"name":"Shin Eun-jung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Shin Eun-jung","tmdb_id":1336527,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kMljH91HGp7HugKi7hRc7xMKl9M.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1336527"},{"name":"Kim Kwang-kyu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Kwang-kyu","tmdb_id":224673,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5X3oJA1NaesYHeX3LfuC7t3j7VV.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/224673"},{"name":"Kim Kang-hoon","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Kang-hoon","tmdb_id":2399088,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1pWaLzjbz5H04mC3Tavfw9mRkNK.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2399088"},{"name":"Jung Hyung-suk","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jung Hyung-suk","tmdb_id":3406347,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/f3vUC7ZDIV